            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I didn't know about the added requirement for `libatomic` - that's good to know about possibly a reason for not doing it.\n\nI think it might be OK though because:\n* I think we only use 32 bit atomics on 32 bit systems\n* we already prefer standard library atomics where they're available and don't give users an way to choose the implementation. I'd expect the standard library will have the same link requirements. That probably means that most users that this affects will already be seeing this problem.\n\nI'm try to check this properly with a 32 bit build if I do end up changing this though.",
